<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gemforest Live-Sparring Service</title>
    <style>
        /* --- WALD-THEME FARBPALETTE --- */
        :root {
            --bg-color: #141f19;       /* Tiefes Tannengrün / fast schwarz */
            --container-bg: #1b2a22;   /* Dunkles Moosgrün für den Inhalt */
            --text-color: #e2ece9;     /* Sanftes, helles Graugrün (augenfreundlich) */
            --accent-green: #4ade80;   /* Frisches Maigrün für Links/Highlights */
            --accent-earth: #b45309;   /* Warmes Erd-Braun für Akzente */
            --border-color: #2d4337;   /* Ast-Grau für Trennlinien */
            --code-bg: #0f1713;         /* Sehr dunkles Grün für Code-Blöcke */
        }

        /* --- BASIS STYLES --- */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            background-color: var(--container-bg);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        /* --- MARKDOWN ELEMENTS STYLING --- */
        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 1.6em;
            margin-bottom: 0.6em;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-earth);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: var(--accent-green);
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2em;
        }

        /* Links */
        a {
            color: var(--accent-green);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s ease-in-out;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--accent-green);
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom-style: solid;
        }

        /* Listen */
        ul, ol {
            margin-bottom: 1.2em;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 0.4em;
        }

        /* Zitate (> in Markdown) */
        blockquote {
            margin: 1.5em 0;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-earth);
            font-style: italic;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        /* Code-Blöcke (``` in Markdown) */
        pre {
            background-color: var(--code-bg);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        code {
            font-family: 'Fira Code', Consolas, Monaco, monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            background-color: var(--code-bg);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #f472b6; /* Leichtes Beeren-Rosa für Inline-Code */
        }

        pre code {
            padding: 0;
            color: #e2ece9;
            background-color: transparent;
        }

        /* Horizontale Linie (--- in Markdown) */
        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--border-color);
            margin: 2.5em 0;
        }

        /* Tabellen */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 1.5em;
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            color: var(--accent-green);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(226, 236, 233, 0.4);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        __CONTENT__
        <footer>
            Generiert aus einer Markdown-Datei • 2026
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
